99790c19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mwJd4vfjK8g</a><br />\n<br />\n成為經典<br />\n<br />\n強強聯手"},{"pid":"c459b4a6b32a690af3c79e628d7e0083f1263a59","tid":2342123,"uid":385667,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"愛若難以放進手裡　何不將這雙手放進心裡"},{"pid":"ee1f9f7a0d39b42b8febaf4edb999479e0acb1d1","tid":2342123,"uid":183576,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:49:01.000Z","msg":"這一場革命最終無人取勝 但請你 請你留低一起作見證<br />\n<br />\n我亦很怕一心軟 會將就得更辛酸<br />\n換到飽暖失去自己一世不甘願<br />\n<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰 留在我血脈身體裏<br />\n<br />\n他出發找最愛 今天也未回來<br />\n<br />\n全世界都有暴動的青年 香港幾時先出現<br />\n<br />\n這是場戰爭但勝利是不可能 犯法為彰顯法制不公允"},{"pid":"f95a64133e355004738520301fa539e3ce15db76","tid":2342123,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"誰介意晚節會不保　笑一笑已蒼老"},{"pid":"a992da195dd39dd63294c1f0521b4fe9cc445b0a","tid":2342123,"uid":354808,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"何日變得只關顧 只關顧 一己的髮膚"},{"pid":"eab1e92a94d2d745bfb45114cdcfa09f7c8bd69b","tid":2342123,"uid":305084,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"祈求風和雨吹我到理想的遠處<br />\n故土沒法跟隨我意願<br />\n但為什麼終於 穿過海灣來到老遠<br />\n卻很想返回我的屋邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32112f0c6d54b6ae8a164c62096e5b9c6501bb1a","tid":2342123,"uid":313963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"像我偏要喜歡鬼火 愛是盲目不過 卻不傻"},{"pid":"8fd62d3f2a971ea794c4f9544d7f543d4d2f71e3","tid":2342123,"uid":375949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"你終於真的離開我 真的不會再愛我<br />\n我以為 我可以裝作不難過 怎麼<br />\n心都碎了 心好痛 後悔還有什麼用<br />\n你都已經 在別人的懷中 接受他的溫柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a03e39c27d275391d11db98a50ebae55b069fc1","tid":2342123,"uid":89823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:50:09.000Z","msg":"然而你選擇做平凡的人<br />\n於是我也就愛上你的人<br />\n甘願我的靈魂 困在這個肉身<br />\n只求能跟你相襯 <br />\n<br />\n然而你已是最平凡的人<br />\n看著多美好心卻那麼笨<br />\n雙手和你碰過 肩膀和你擦過<br />\n靈魂卻無法相認"},{"pid":"22bd4d83e8410dace56a63889ccc456280e826f7","tid":2342123,"uid":270995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"祝你在亂流下平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f18e3315e38a748e91b969d67e5d0a3717292cc","tid":2342123,"uid":360821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"在世間漂泊 孤身仿似浮雲<br />\n心底裏 每思親 添百感<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a5f0004bbb118e9f65cb0fa116e6e5d9890421","tid":2342123,"uid":136883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:01:19.000Z","msg":"醜惡在於 赤子的胸懷<br />\n難敵這紛擾世態 為理想或求生在捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868cce6c650b54214e788e99438fb742d224f5c6","tid":2342123,"uid":169819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"未來只看著你 微笑中斑點會皺起"},{"pid":"24fa12241e7420a05ac99265715793f0c70a885b","tid":2342123,"uid":307644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:19:32.000Z","msg":"香港地要表態直言要上街"},{"pid":"fa0077de3073781f917cc6b25cd56324013a0157","tid":2342123,"uid":4059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:32:56.000Z","msg":"並未在一起亦無從離棄 不用淪為伴侶 別尋事惹非<br />\n<br />\n-失憶蝴蝶"},{"pid":"3e56229114a4d665eab9949b25184a9569065eff","tid":2342123,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:35:20.000Z","msg":"無愛可失 得不到相戀別說失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塵埃落定"},{"pid":"b263ca5a7f842272e28ea0e0067df21b9225ef61","tid":2342123,"uid":39253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T18:38:15.000Z","msg":"而我愛你 <br />\n而愛無法撐起"},{"pid":"91f777e9c31d60dc6696ac00b9